  "notes": "Naomi Tewksbury's grandmother. Born 1699 in Marblehead, Essex County, MA — one of the earliest known ancestors, born in the 1600s. Puritan. Married Jonathan Tewksbury (1695-) on October 30, 1717 in Marblehead. Son Richard Tewksbury (1729-1775). Son Richard died Nov 12, 1775. Mary died 1776 in Danvers, MA at approximately age 77. Buried in a Puritan burial ground."
